Interface Map

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Map_Cadance, Map_CS151, Map_DIAMOND, Map_FILLED, Map_Nothing, Map_OWO, Map_Random
    public interface Map
    I think the ability to add different maps is an example of a strategy pattern In this case, the way we generate maps can benefit from variants of an algorithm. Clients can replace the map that is generated with their own custom versions. All they need is to return an arraylist of blocks, which this interface ensures.

    Leo_Le
